**The AI Angle:** As noted in industry analysis, "AI is changing HR and every CHRO needs help." The company that can guide HR leaders through AI adoption across *all* domains—not just learning—will own the relationship. HR.com's pan-HR audience combined with ATD's deep L&D and AI-focused content creates an unrivaled advisory position.

